        <title>hugo&#43;obsidian打造最强博客</title>
        <link>https://eatmoreduck.github.io/p/hugo-obsidian%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
